1. Reading CSV file using pandas library of python 
2. Mapping international ,voice_mail_plan and churn fields of data to true and false.


3. Divide data on basis of churn field of data as data_true and data_false
4. Divide data_true and data_false into train and test data such that train/test = 0.8/0.2


5. Making Gaussian classifier using  GaussianNB library 
6. Fitting classifier using train_data and finding result for test_data
7. Calculating TP,TN,FN,FP for calculating enteries for confusion matrix
8. Calculate accuracy, precision and recall using enteries of confusion matrix


9. Making SVM classifier using sklearn library 
10. Fitting classifier using train_data and finding result for test_data
11. Calculating TP,TN,FN,FP for calculating enteries for confusion matrix
12. Calculate accuracy, precision and recall using enteries of confusion matrix


13. Making Desicion tree classifier using sklearn library 
14. Fitting classifier using train_data and finding result for test_data
15. Calculating TP,TN,FN,FP for calculating enteries for confusion matrix
16. Calculate accuracy, precision and recall using enteries of confusion matrix


17. Comparing different classifier on basis of accuracy, precision and recall to give best classifier
   
 best classifier 'Decision Tree Classifier'**.
 maximum performance achieved by the classifier:
 
     ACCURACY:  0.889110889111
     PRECISION:  0.676056338028
